summary: I am a professional, hospitality-driven individual with ethics, moral responsibility and gastronomy as my core values. Due to my perseverance and curiosity, I have gained useful experience from; cafe's, restaurants, the service industry, hotels, volunteer work, events and retail. My compassion and interest in those physically less able than myself has brought me the opportunity of volunteering for children. Being open-minded, I am passionate about seeing, not only the surface, but what lies within. My hobbies include; sports, music and reading, to name a few.
